\b\fs36 \cf0 Prerequisites
\fs24 \

\b0 To build these frameworks you need Xcode 3.2 or later (tested only with Xcode 4.2 to 4.5). Xcode is available free on the {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "http://itunes.apple.com/us/app/xcode/id422352214?mt=12&ls=1"}}{\fldrslt Mac App Store}}.\
In order to build cURL you also need {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "http://cmake.org/cmake/resources/software.html."}}{\fldrslt CMake}} installed. If using the package from the website, make sure you select 'Install Command Line Links' when asked at the end of the install.\
\

